# Concept

Trigger-Grid-Engine is not a typical Excel tool.

It is an engine.

Instead of writing logic in code,
logic is placed on the grid using triggers.

Cells do not contain colors or behavior.
They only contain simple codes.

Everything else is resolved by the engine.

---

## Philosophy

Pick the logic.
Place it on the grid.

---

## Why this matters

- No hardcoded row/column logic
- Fully data-driven
- Rebuildable from saved state
- Visual and programmable at the same time
